280
00:22:52,371 --> 00:22:53,872
What does that have to do with her?

281
00:22:56,291 --> 00:22:57,209
Her father,

282
00:22:57,292 --> 00:22:59,628
Yun Seong-jun, must've taken my tablet.

283
00:23:00,253 --> 00:23:02,339
