306
00:24:15,996 --> 00:24:17,372
That guy told me

307
00:24:17,456 --> 00:24:19,040
that Yun Seong-jun said

308
00:24:19,124 --> 00:24:21,501
he had to go meet his daughter.

309
00:24:23,587 --> 00:24:24,588
The tablet has...

310
00:24:26,673 --> 00:24:30,302
